  "description": "This image showcases a small, cascading waterfall flowing over moss-covered rocks in a lush forest setting. The water is clear and appears to be moving rapidly down a steep, rocky incline. The rocks themselves are predominantly dark, but are heavily adorned with vibrant green moss, creating a striking contrast. Ferns and other verdant foliage fill the foreground and surround the waterfall, adding to the dense, natural environment. Several trees, also covered in moss, are visible, framing the scene and reinforcing the sense of a secluded, ancient woodland. A fallen log is visible near the bottom of the frame. The lighting is diffused, suggesting an overcast day or a heavily shaded area within the forest.",
